{
  "stem": "13911.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just thought you eat well-- as well as you can afford-- and that was enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then times became modern, and inoculations-- inoculations, you know, started taking place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they created that-- it was called-- can I say it in Polish?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Towarzystwo Ochrony Zdrowia, which means a Society for Health Care-- health care would be the right translation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, whenever inoculation, you would go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they would tell you how to take care of your health and whatever modern thing-- whatever modern method came out so to make people aware how to behave and what to do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were mentioning your father went to this--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father belonged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they had their own-- as I said, there are all kinds of little-- sprang-- you know, branched out, because maybe people lived a little further.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody would take anything that was mobile on a holiday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had to reach it closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe you were old or sick or-- so you had, like, nearby, in a private-- maybe not a home, but-- yes-- specially designed for it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was called a [? shtiebel. ?]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I played.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I fasted when I was very young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I fasted a half a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on I fasted the whole day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I attended public school, which was seven years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Russians occupied our, our part of Poland-- the Polish Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From '39 to '41, I went to a Russian school for two years until '41.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Until Hitler attacked again and the war started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to that middle school, which was all in Russian, you know, done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I liked religion.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very good in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe because it sounded like-- or mythology, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
